{"tid":1900841,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"嘩LISA姐返參加陸版我獨自生活","createTime":"2020-02-27T12:41:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T08:49:32.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"017eb27aa5b3c2607b9a77fe5fdc0532970a0d56","tid":1900841,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T12:41:34.000Z","msg":"網爆陸版《我獨自生活》 名單外流驚見Lisa、賴冠霖！<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4727/d4727077.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4727%2Fd4727077.jpg&h=b6ae9b41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲韓粽《我獨自生活》深受觀眾喜愛。（圖／翻攝自ig）<br />\n<br />\n記者黃庠棻／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n南韓綜藝《我獨自生活》是一檔觀察型的節目，窺探演藝圈中獨自生活的藝人們的日常生活，2013年開播至今已有7年，每次嘉賓登場總是會引起許多話題，甚至登上熱搜，27日微博上更流傳了該節目即將推出大陸版，連卡司名單都一併外流，造成網友熱議。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4727/d4727079.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4727%2Fd4727079.jpg&h=a3248973&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲陸版《我獨自生活》嘉賓名單驚見Lisa。（圖／翻攝自ig）<br />\n<br />\n微博27日流傳著大陸影視公司「愛奇藝」即將製作陸版《我獨自生活》的消息，連主持人與嘉賓名單都一起公開，MC的部分由謝楠、楊迪以及金靖擔任，每一集將會有4為嘉賓出演，透過鏡頭公開他們私底下生活的面貌，其中跟韓版有些差別的地方就是，一季將有10位以上的來賓，觀察的過程中彼此將會有些互動，穿插對方的生活。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4727/d4727078.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4727%2Fd4727078.jpg&h=6f8e89ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲陸版《我獨自生活》嘉賓名單驚見賴冠霖。（圖／翻攝自ig）<br />\n<br />\n然而，嘉賓卡司一排開，竟然出現了Black Pink的成員Lisa以及Wanna One的賴冠霖，讓大批粉絲相當驚喜，另外還有在大陸非常火紅的范丞丞、小鬼、進軍好萊塢的演員景甜、電競選手Uzi、張炘橙、金靖、孫藝洲、美娜等人，節目組希望透過不同性別、年齡、職業，激盪出全新的火花。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4727/d4727081.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4727%2Fd4727081.jpg&h=af785d17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲陸版《我獨自生活》主持人、嘉賓名單流出。（圖／翻攝自微博）<br />\n<br />\n此外，陸版《我獨自生活》製作消息公開後，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有粉絲疑惑「為何Lisa不參加韓版的，反而參加陸版的？」、「Lisa不是住在宿舍嗎？」</span></strong>形成另一波討論潮，另外也有不少人質疑「又是抄襲」，對此節目組則清楚寫下是由南韓「原班團隊加盟」，雖然未經過證實，但已有許多觀眾表示期待。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4727/d4727080.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4727%2Fd4727080.jpg&h=63d25d89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲陸版《我獨自生活》寫明是用「加盟」的方式播出。（圖／翻攝自微博）"},{"pid":"41274ecd9cd26121aa6c2c70b01de03c3cb026e0","tid":1900841,"uid":256952,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T12:42:24.000Z","msg":"Lisa:我是中國泰省人"},{"pid":"7af6d3b8866b1d28f641c1bdf85977e19f2f3a87","tid":1900841,"uid":87394,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T12:46:13.000Z","msg":"依家唔係買版權黎拍<br />\n係直接成team買黎拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bedc473b9673bde7c1944c9962d8e72eac5e5743","tid":1900841,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7af6d3b8866b1d28f641c1bdf85977e19f2f3a87","tid":1900841,"uid":87394,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T12:46:13.000Z","msg":"依家唔係買版權黎拍<br />\n係直接成team買黎拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T12:47:42.000Z","msg":"RM好似都係 不過賣左幾季就中止左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ffb54a2bceffa4a2a07bd93b81ee31bc14921a1","tid":1900841,"uid":262223,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T12:49:33.000Z","msg":"就咁望個標題仲以為係汪阿姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cd5688c6932c0887c573cb363df81e24207a936","tid":1900841,"uid":117802,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T13:05:02.000Z","msg":"范丞丞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會唔會播埋佢家姐范冰冰同王岐山嘅生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c56d2b25a90339e14411bd6bab643ebb421f0fe","tid":1900841,"uid":267485,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T13:07:51.000Z","msg":